metadata.name: Ava and Elara
metadata.description:
Ava and Elara, two Albino Woman Elf Astornot, were on a mission to explore the far reaches of the galaxy. 

They had been traveling for weeks, hopping from one star system to the next, when they detected a strange reading on their scanners. It was a planet, unlike any they had ever seen before.

As they descended through the planet's atmosphere, they could see that it was a world covered in glittering crystal formations. 

The ground beneath their feet was smooth and translucent, reflecting the light from the nearby star. Ava and Elara marveled at the beauty of the planet, but they also knew that they had to be cautious. 

They were the first beings to set foot on this world, and they had no idea what kind of life they might encounter.
